###

// Empty username
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": null,
    "password": "thisispassword",
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "favoriteTeam": "Arsenal",
    "avatar": 1
}

###

// Short password ( Should fail ) 

POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "fail",
    "password": "as",
    "email": "fail@test.com",
    "favoriteTeam": "Arsenal",
    "avatar": 1
}

###

